data.description: Beautiful two story home in Wyndhaven subdivision 4 bedroom, two and 1/2 baths. Finished basement.  Roof 2016, Sump pump 2020 battery backup. Water Heater 2016, A/C 2014, Furnace 2018, Deck 2021.  All newer whirlpool appliances 2019. Radon Mitigated.  First and second floor just professionally painted. Updated kitchen and hardwood floors throughout the first floor.  Newer deck. Second floor laundry. Fully fenced backyard.  All schools in town.  Seller offering a $2500 flooring allowance.
